features: Clear Front Pocket Design : INFUN 3 prong pocket folders feature a top-loading transparent pocket on the front that you can use to place a customized cover or file theme. This helps you identify the types of internal documents more quickly and improves your work or learning efficiency. In addition, the front pocket can also be used to display a company or personal brand logo or design, enhancing the folder's professional and personalized appearance.

Heavy Duty Plastic Pocket Folders with Prongs : Our folder is made of durable 0.5mm thick plastic material and has 2 pockets and 3 prongs, as well as a card slot for holding business cards or student ID. It's the perfect choice for organizing letter-sized documents, files, and papers, and keeping them secure and easy to access.

Secure Organization with Stay-Put Tabs: Our plastic folder with brads are designed with two sturdy stay-put tabs to keep your documents secure and in place during transport,preventing them from slipping or falling out of the folder. This ensures your important files stay organized and protected, allowing you to move confidently between home, work, and school without worrying about misplacing or losing them.

Add Some Color to Your Workday: Each pack includes six folders in vibrant color of red, blue, yellow, green, pink, and purple. These fun colors not only brighten up your workspace but also make it easy to organize and categorize your files.

Wide Applications - Measuring 9.5 x 11.7 inches, our pocket folders with prongs can hold a large amount of loose documents and hole-punched papers, making them ideal for a variety of settings. They are perfect for educational purposes, school work, teaching and homework, office tasks, projects, presentations, as well as archiving, filing, and storage.
